"title": "5391: letters",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5391",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A form of written communication often used for the transfer of instruction, information and advice or important news.</p>\n<h2>Letters of encouragement or exhortation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:30\">EST 9:30</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:22\">HEB 13:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:11\">2CH 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:12\">2CH 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:1\">ISA 39:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:1\">JER 29:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:23-Acts15:31\">ACT 15:23–15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:9\">1CO 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:9-2Cor10:11\">2CO 10:9–10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:16\">COL 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:27\">1TH 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:1\">2PE 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Malicious, threatening or devious letters</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:14-2Sam11:15\">2SA 11:14–11:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1-2Thess2:2\">2TH 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:8\">1KI 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:14\">2KI 19:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:14\">ISA 37:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:17\">2CH 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:7\">EZR 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:5\">NEH 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:19\">NEH 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:1-Acts9:2\">ACT 9:1–9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:5\">ACT 22:5</a></p>\n<h2>Letters of authorisation or identification</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:11\">EZR 7:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:3\">1CO 16:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:5-2Kgs5:6\">2KI 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:7-Neh2:9\">NEH 2:7–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:25\">ACT 23:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:33-Acts23:34\">ACT 23:33–23:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:1\">2CO 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Affairs of state conducted by letter</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:22\">EST 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:1-2Kgs10:3\">2KI 10:1–10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:6-2Kgs10:7\">2KI 10:6–10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:6-Ezra5:7\">EZR 5:6–5:7</a></p>\n<h2>Letters as invitations to worship</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:1\">2CH 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:6\">2CH 30:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:20\">EST 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:26\">EST 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:29\">EST 9:29</a></p>\n<h2>Letters attributed to specific authors</h2>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1\">ROM 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1\">1CO 1:1</a> <em>with Sosthenes</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1\">2CO 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1\">PHP 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:1\">COL 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1\">PHM 1:1</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:1\">GAL 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1\">EPH 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:1\">1TH 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:1\">2TH 1:1</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:1\">1TI 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:1\">2TI 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:1\">TIT 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:15-2Pet3:16\">2PE 3:15–3:16</a></p>\n<h3>James</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:1\">JAS 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Peter</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">1PE 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1\">2PE 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Jude</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:1\">JUD 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:1\">REV 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:8\">REV 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:12\">REV 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:18\">REV 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1\">REV 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:7\">REV 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>Letters written by a secretary</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:22\">ROM 16:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">1PE 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>Letters of the alphabet</h2>\n<h3>The letter of the law</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Paul writing in large letters</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:11\">GAL 6:11</a></p>",
